Author: John Wong
Date: 01/24/2020

usage: gen_cvt_partition.py [-h] [-g GRID_FILE] centroids [centroids ...]

Assign MPAS cell points to convex partitions specified by centroids.

positional arguments:
centroids     Text file(s) containing cartesian coordinates for partitioning
              centroids

optional arguments:
-h, --help    show this help message and exit
-g GRID_FILE  NetCDF file containing {x,y,z}Cell. (default: grid.nc)
